OL,5, Former Tory deputy chairman Lee        
OL,6, Anderson has been suspended from the   
OL,7, party after "refusing to apologise" for
OL,8, comments aimed at Sadiq Khan.          
OL,10,FThe Conservative Ashfield MP told GB   
OL,11,FNews on Friday "Islamists" had "got    
OL,12,Fcontrol" of the mayor of London.       
OL,14,FResponding on Saturday, Mr Khan        
OL,15,Fdescribed the remarks as "pouring fuel 
OL,16,Fon the fire of anti-Muslim hatred".    
OL,18,FLosing the Conservative whip           
OL,19,Fessentially expels Mr Anderson from his
OL,20,Fparty in Parliament.                   
